column27: In the trail management UI it was too easy to make a mistake and edit the wrong trail. Usability could be improved. Ability to easily edit the shelf layout would make possible to safely change shelf layout during the competition. Important to make clear to the public the robot goals during each trail and their success at each goal.

column27: Make the process easier, even if it's just better documentation. The complexity of posting data was made worse by technical issues during the event.
